BY LINUS CHIBUIKE HOODLUMS have set the Dutse Makaranta Police station ablaze in Abuja. The police station, in the Kubwa area of the Federal Capital Territory, was reportedly burnt down during a clash between hoodlums and policemen. One person was feared killed in the incident. It was gathered that while trying to disperse a crowd that gathered outside the station, a policeman had allegedly fired a gunshot, which killed the victim. Details laterâ€¦ 